f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshow%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20it%20does%20not%20have%20any%20human%20remains%20on%20display%2C%20according%20to%20the%20museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20tribal%20officials%20and%20repatriation%20activists%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancient-artifacts-countries-are-still-fighting-over-history-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%20for%20the%20speedier%20return%20of%20Native%20remains%20and%20objects%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Archaeologists%20and%20museum%20collectors%20looted%20tribal%20remains%20from%20ancient%20graves%2C%20homes%2C%20and%20worship%20sites%20throughout%20the%201800s%2C%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flatter-day-saints-church-mormon-native-indian-placement-program-icwa-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20pushed%20Native%20Americans%20from%20their%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuseums%20across%20the%20nation%20have%20had%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20remove%20Native%20objects%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20new%20rules%20or%20risk%20violating%20them%20by%20leaving%20the%20objects%20on%20display.%20The%20Peabody%20Museum%20of%20Archaeology%20and%20Ethnology%20at%20Harvard%20University%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-university-holding-on-remains-7000-indigenous-people-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20holds%20onto%20thousands%20of%20Native%20American%20remains%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20not%20announced%20how%20it%20will%20respond%20to%20the%20latest%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rules%20are%20the%20latest%20effort%20by%20the%20federal%20government%20to%20ensure%20museums%20are%20giving%20tribes%20the%20proper%20consideration%20over%20Native%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20people%20were%20treating%20that%20relationship%20with%20respect%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20there%20probably%20wouldn't%20be%20a%20need%20for%20