ers%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Congress%20made%20a%20beeline%20for%20Ayodhya%20on%20Makar%20Sankranti%20today%2C%20notwithstanding%20their%20Central%20leaders'%20refusal%20to%20attend%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20or%20the%20party%20line%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20are%20using%20the%20event%20to%20gain%20political%20milage%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20When%20asked%2C%20they%20indicated%20that%20it%20was%20a%20personal%20visit.%20%26quot%3BLord%20Ram%20belongs%20to%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20refrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20UP%20Congress%20have%20already%20declared%20that%20they%20would%20attend%20the%20consecration%20event.%20Today%2C%20they%20took%20a%20dip%20in%20Saryu%20river%2C%20had%20the%20Darshan%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20and%20went%20to%20Hanumangarhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20their%20action%20was%20not%20a%20deviation%20from%20the%20party%20line%2C%20UP%20leader%20Avinash%20Pande%20said%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20openly%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthose%20who%20have%20faith%20can%20go%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20invited%20anyone%20to%20attend%2C%20nor%20are%20we%20stopping%20anyone%20from%20attending%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20quoted%20Mr%20Kharge%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20against%20the%20way%20this%20event%20is%20being%20politicised%20and%20used%20to%20create%20rift%20in%20society%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Haryana%20Congress%20leader%20Deepender%20Singh%20Hooda%2C%20who%20was%20among%20the%20UP%20contingent%20that%20included%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Ajai%20Rai%20and%20senior%20leader%20Avdesh%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20insisted%20that%20he%20was%20a%20regular%20visitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20last%20year%20too.%20Today%20on%20the%20auspicious%20occasion%20of%20Makar%20Sankranti%2C%20I%20have%20to%20gaze%20upon%20Ram%20Lalla%20and%20seek%20his%20blessings.%20This%20is%20how%20I%20recharge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20party%20line%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20take%20any%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20question%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BRam%20does%20not%20belong%20to%20any%20particular%20person.%20He%20belongs%20to%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20declined%20the%20invite%20for%20January%2022%20temple%20consecration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReligion%20is%20a%20personal%20matter.%20But%20the%20RSS%2FBJP%20have%20long%20made%20a%20political%20project%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20inauguration%20of%20the%20incomplete%20temple%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20has%20been%20obviously%20brought%20forward%20for%20electoral%20gain%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20statement%20from%20senior%20party%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20BJP%20erupted%20in%20vociferous%20condemnation%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20it%20was%20not%20the%20party's%20intention%20to%20hurt%20anyone's%20religious%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20issue%20is%20this%20-%20what%20work%20is%20the%20PM%20doing%20to%20ensure%20jobs%20for%20the%20public%3F%20What%20steps%20is%20he%20taking%20to%20control%20inflation%3F%20What%20is%20he%20doing%20for%20poor%20people%E2%80%A6%20People%20having%20faith%20can%20go%20(to%20the%20temple)%20today...%20they%20can%20go%20tomorrow%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20and%20more%20than%206%2C000%20people%20are%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20mega%20event%20of%20January%2022%20%E2%80%93%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20leade