%20that%20such%20threats%20have%20a%20direct%20bearing%20on%20India's%20energy%20and%20economic%20interest%20as%20he%20underlined%20that%20this%20%26quot%3Bfraught%20situation%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20to%20the%20benefit%20of%20any%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20also%20been%20recently%20a%20perceptible%20increase%20in%20threats%20to%20the%20safety%20of%20maritime%20commercial%20traffic%20in%20this%20important%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20press%20statement%20after%20wide-ranging%20talks%20with%20Iranian%20counterpart%20Hossein%20Amirabdollahian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stressed%20that%20it's%20important%20that%20this%20issue%20be%20%26quot%3Bspeedily%20addressed%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20targeting%20of%20merchant%20vessels%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20-%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20trade%20routes%20-%20by%20Iranian-backed%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20rebels%20amid%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20even%20seen%20some%20attacks%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20India.%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20great%20concern%20to%20the%20international%20community.%20Obviously%2C%20it%20also%20has%20a%20direct%20bearing%20on%20India's%20energy%20and%20economic%20interests.%20This%20fraught%20situation%20is%20not%20to%20the%20benefit%20of%20any%20party%20and%20this%20must%20be%20clearly%20recognised%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20a%20missile%20fired%20by%20Houthis%20struck%20a%20US-owned%20ship%20just%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Yemen%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden.%20A%20day%20earlier%2C%20Houthi%20fired%20an%20anti-ship%20cruise%20missile%20toward%20an%20American%20destroyer%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20the%20UK%20last%20week%20launched%20air%20strikes%20targeting%20the%20Houthi%20positions%20in%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20unfolding%20situation%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%20The%20Indian%20Navy%20has%20already%20enhanced%20deployment%20of%20its%20frontline%20ships%20and%20surveillance%20aircraft%20for%20maritime%20security%20operations%20in%20view%20of%20the%20maritime%20environment%20in%20the%20critical%20sea%20lanes%20including%20the%20North%20and%20Central%20Arabian%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EmR%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20is%20here%20as%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20high-level%20exchanges%20between%20the%20two%20sides%2C%20also%20said%20that%20both%20India%20and%20Iran%20are%20concerned%20about%20recent%20events%20in%20West%20Asia%20and%20emphasise%20the%20importance%20of%20preventing%20further%20escalation%20of%20violence%20and%20hostilities%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20concerning%26quot%3B%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20was%20naturally%20a%20subject%20of%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%2C%20especially%20that%20of%20women%20and%20children%20was%20our%20primary%20focus.%20There%20is%20a%20visible%20humanitarian%20crisis%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20sustainable%20humanitarian%20corridors%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20and%20welcomed%20the%20international%20community's%20efforts%20in%20that%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20itself%20has%20delivered%20shipments%20of%20relief%20material%20to%20Gaza%20and%20contributed%20to%20the%20UNRWA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20Palestine%2C%20Jaishankar%20reiterated%20India's%20long%20standing%20support%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution%2C%20where%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20are%20able%20to%20live%20freely%20in%20an%20independent%20country%20within%20secure%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20stressed%20on%20the%20need%20for%20all%20parties%20to%20avoid%20provocative%20and%20escalatory%20actions%2C