ian%20aid%20and%20medical%20evacuations%20for%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20remote%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDomestic%20politics%20of%20Maldives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Muizzu%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20pro-China%20leader%2C%20a%20departure%20from%20his%20predecessors%20who%20pursued%20a%20pro-India%20policy.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20slogans%20for%20his%20campaign%20was%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Out'.%20The%20coalition%20government%20of%20the%20People's%20National%20Congress%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives%20party%20is%20currently%20following%20the%20pro-China%20policy%20to%20remove%20what%20they%20call%20the%20Indian%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Presidential%20election%20held%20in%20Maldives%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September%2C%20supporters%20of%20the%20People's%20National%20Congress%20of%20President%20Muizzu%20had%20pushed%20a%20narrative%20that%20the%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih-led%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%20was%20influenced%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20formal%20demand%20for%20troop%20removal%20was%20first%20made%20around%20two%20months%20ago%20--%20shortly%20after%20the%20Muizzu%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%20September%2C%20riding%20on%20an%20anti-India%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnti-India%20build-up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20gift%20of%20two%20military%20Dhruv%20Advanced%20Light%20Helicopters%20helicopters%20to%20Maldives%20for%20rescue%20ops%20have%20been%20portrayed%20as%20creation%20of%20military%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20agreement%20for%20the%20UTF%20Harbour%20Project%20agreement%2C%20signed%20in%20February%202021%20--%20under%20which%20India%20was%20to%20develop%20and%20maintain%20a%20harbour%20and%20dockyard%20at%20Uthuru%20Thilafalhu%20near%20Maldives%20capital%20Mal%C3%A9%20--%20has%20been%20a%20subject%20of%20intense%20speculation.%20A%20section%20of%20local%20media%20claimed%20that%20the%20project%20would%20eventually%20lead%20to%20the%20building%20of%20an%20Indian%20naval%20base%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFuelled%20by%20social%20media%2C%20a%20diplomatic%20row%20with%20India%20started%20as%20Maldivian%20ministers%20made%20derogatory%20comments%20following%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20widely%20circulated%20post%20about%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Lakshadweep%20islands.%20Three%20ministers%20who%20made%20harsh%20comments%2C%20were%2C%20however%2C%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Muizzu's%20demand%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20Indian%20troops%20was%20also%20made%20days%20after%20his%20visit%20to%20China%2C%20when%20the%20two%20nations%20upgraded%20their%20relationship%20to%20a%20comprehensive%20strategic%20cooperative%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20interested%20in%20expanding%20its%20influence%20in%20Maldives%20owing%20to%20its%20strategic%20position%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%20The%20islands%20are%20located%20on%20the%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20maritime%20trade%20highways%20through%20which%20nearly%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20China's%20oil%20imports%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaldives%20and%20China%20have%20signed%2020%20important%20agreements%20during%20President%20Muizzu's%20visit.%20China%20has%20given%20Male%20an%20aid%20of%20130%20million%20dollars%20which%20will%20be%20spent%20on%20the%20development%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20India%20be%20concerned%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foreign%20ministry%20is%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20Male's%20demand%20for%20troop%20withdrawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20foreign%20minister%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20has%20warned%20about%20the%20increasing%20proximity%20between%20China%20and%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20China%20has%20been%20attempting%20to%20expand%20its%20influence%20throughout%20our%20periphery.%20They%20have%20been%20increasingly%20influential%20in%20everyone%20of%20our%20neighbouring%20countries%2C%20everyone%2C%20without%20exception%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705331220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fc1nt5v2g_mohamed-muizzu_625x300_09_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-maldives-president-mohamed-muizzu-is-talking-tough-explainer-4868525%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maldives%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu's%20demand%20that%20India%20withdraw%20its%20troops%20stationed%20in%20the%20country%20by%20March%2015%20is%20the%20newest%20in%20the%20anti-India%20rhetoric%20in%20the%20island%20nation%20that%20has%20started%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-maldives-president-mohamed-muizzu-is-talking-tough-explainer-4868525%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-maldives-president-mohamed-muizzu-is-talking-tough-explainer-4868525%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-maldives-president-mohamed-muizzu-is-talking-tough-explainer-4868525%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Photos%20%7C%20'We%20Want%20to%20Go%20Back%20Home'%3A%20Inside%20a%20Relief%20Camp%20in%20Manipur's%20Imphal%20West%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15194349%2FSana.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImphal%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20residents%20of%20the%20Lamboikhongnangkhong%20relief%20camp%20in%20Imphal%20West%2C%20life%20has%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%20since%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20flee%20their%20homes%20after%20ethnic%20violence%20erupted%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20Trade%20and%20Expo%20Centre%20has%20been%20serving%20as%20the%