)%20today%20issued%20guidelines%20to%20handle%20chaotic%20situations%20as%20was%20seen%20yesterday%20due%20to%20fog%20in%20Delhi%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DGCA%20in%20the%20standard%20operating%20procedure%20(SOP)%20for%20%26quot%3Bfacilities%20to%20be%20provided%20to%20passengers%20by%20airlines%20due%20to%20denied%20boarding%2C%20cancellation%20of%20flights%20and%20delays%20in%20flights%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20that%20airlines%20may%20cancel%20flights%20that%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20delayed%20or%20%26quot%3Bconsequentially%20delayed%26quot%3B%20beyond%20three%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DGCA%20said%20all%20airlines%20must%20follow%20the%20SOP%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20extraordinary%20circumstances%20beyond%20the%20control%20of%20airlines%2C%20the%20provisions%20of%20these%20rules%20are%20not%20applicable%2C%20the%20DGCA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SOPs%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAirlines%20shall%20be%20required%20to%20publish%20accurate%20real-time%20information%20regarding%20delays%20of%20their%20flights%2C%20which%20shall%20be%20published%20on%3A%20the%20respective%20website%20of%20the%20airline%3B%20through%20advance%20information%20to%20affected%20passengers%20by%20SMS%2FWhatsApp%20and%20email%3B%20display%20of%20updated%20information%20regarding%20flight%20delays%20to%20passengers%20waiting%20at%20airports%2C%20and%20appropriate%20sensitisation%20of%20the%20airline%20staff%20at%20airports%20to%20suitably%20communicate%20with%20and%20continuously%20guide%20and%20inform%20passengers%20about%20flight%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmooth%20coordination%20in%20Delhi%20airport%20broke%20down%20yesterday%20after%20hundreds%20of%20passengers%20of%20delayed%20flights%20demanded%20answers%20from%20the%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stressful%20day%20also%20saw%20the%20passenger%20of%20an%20IndiGo%20flight%20attacking%20a%20pilot%20inside%20the%20plane%20while%20it%20was%20on%20the%20tarmac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20in%20a%20statement%20today%20said%20it%20regrets%20the%20disruption%20to%20operations%20arising%20from%20the%20last%20few%20days'%20dense%20fog%20in%20north%20India%2C%20including%20at%20%26quot%3Bour%20main%20Delhi%20hub%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20some%20diversions%20and%20desynchronisation%20of%20aircraft%20and%20crew%20rotations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20Aviation%20Minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20today%20said%20they%20have%20taken%20steps%20to%20avoid%20similar%20circumstances%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20Delhi%20witnessed%20unprecedented%20fog%20wherein%20visibility%20fluctuated%20for%20several%20hours%2C%20and%20at%20times%2C%20dropped%20to%20zero%20between%205%20am%20and%209%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Scindia%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20authorities%2C%20therefore%2C%20were%20compelled%20to%20enforce%20a%20shut-down%20of%20operations%20for%20some%20time%20even%20on%20CAT%20III%20runways%20(CAT%20III%20runways%20cannot%20handle%20zero-visibility%20operations).%20The%20decision%20was%20taken%20keeping%20passenger%20safety%20in%20mind%2C%20which%20remains%20the%20foremost%20priority%20for%20all%20in%20the%20aviation%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705329900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Far695pi8_delhi-airport-chaos_625x300_15_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fairlines-to-cancel-delayed-flights-new-rules-amid-fog-chaos-4868276%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20regulator%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%20today%20issued%20guidelines%20to%20handle%20chaotic%20situations%20as%20was%20seen%20yesterday%20due%20to%20fog%20in%20Delhi%20airport.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fairlines-to-cancel-delayed-flights-new-rules-amid-fog-chaos-48