play%20(Ranji%20game%20against%20Andhra).%20I%20came%2C%20and%20I%20executed%2C%20so%20I%20am%20happy%20with%20what%20I'm%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20that%20is%20not%20in%20my%20control%2C%20I%20can't%20be%20focusing%20on%20that.%20Coming%20here%20and%20winning%20the%20match%20was%20my%20focus%20and%20that's%20what%20we%20did%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Iyer%20told%20reporters%20after%20Mumbai's%20emphatic%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIyer%2C%20after%20a%20poor%20series%20in%20South%20Africa%20where%20he%20seemed%20like%20a%20'walking%20wicket'%2C%20was%20instructed%20by%20selectors%20to%20go%20and%20play%20Ranji%20Trophy%20for%20Mumbai%20as%20he%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Test%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIyer%20scored%20a%20run-a-ball%2048%20as%20Andhra%20bowlers%20tried%20to%20exploit%20his%20weakness%20against%20short%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20Test%20series%2C%20Iyer%20replied%20he%20isn't%20looking%20that%20far%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20take%20one%20match%20at%20a%20time%2C%20not%20think%20about%20five-match%20Test%20series.%20The%20team%20is%20only%20for%20the%20first%20two%20games.%20The%20motto%20would%20be%20to%20perform%20in%20the%20first%20two%20games%20and%20then%20look%20forward%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIyer%2C%20a%20master%20player%20of%20slow%20bowling%2C%20is%20expecting%20turners%20against%20England%20with%20first%20Test%20starting%20on%20January%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Iyer%20found%20most%20satisfying%20during%20145%20plus%20overs%20of%20fielding%2C%20across%20two%20Andhra%20innings%2C%20was%20his%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20assuming%20that%20we%20would%20be%20getting%20turning%20wickets%20against%20England.%20But%20other%20than%20that%2C%20it%20was%20just%20for%20my%20match%20fitness%2C%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20field%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%20that's%20what%20mainly%20I%20was%20focusing%20on%20because%20especially%20after%20my%20injury%2C%20it%20has%20been%20tough%20for%20me%20to%20stick%20on%20the%20outfield%20for%20long.%20So%20this%20was%20great%20practice%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIyer's%20Test%20career%20is%20at%20the%20crossroads%20and%20there%20are%20no%20guarantees%20if%20he%20would%20be%20able%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20his%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20fun.%20I%20love%20competition%2C%20and%20when%20competition%20is%20there%2C%20you%20face%20more%20challenges.%20And%20that's%20what%20I%20thrive%20on%20personally.%20So%20I%20enjoy%20having%20competition%20around%20because%20then%20you%20can%20go%20at%20each%20other%20and%20also%20against%20the%20opponents%20to%20show%20your%20talent%20and%20skills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWon't%20change%20his%20batting%20style%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Ranji%20match%20against%20Andhra%20in%20which%20Mumbai%20cruised%20to%2010-wicket%20victory%20over%20Andhra%2C%20Iyer%20said%20that%20he%20would%20attack%20irrespective%20of%20match%20situation%20just%20like%20he%20did%20on%20the%20first%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20play%20attacking%20irrespective%20of%20the%20situation.%20And%20also%20when%20you%20bowl%20negative%2C%20when%20you%20bowl%20safe%20and%20defensive%20at%20the%20start%2C%20you%20want%20to%20score%20runs%20and%20you%20need%20to%20take%20your%20team%20through%20up%20to%20a%20certain%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that%20was%20my%20mindset%20and%20that's%20why%20stuck%20with.%20Yeah%2C%20I%20was%20happy%20irrespective%20of%20the%20score%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705328880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffu8eh54o_shreyas-iyer-afp_625x300_03_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsomething-that-shreyas-iyer-breaks-silence-on-snub-for-india-vs-afghanistan-t20i-series-4868275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20after%