0if%20Orry%20were%20to%20write%20one.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftwinkle-khannas-fascination-for-orry-and-her-interest-in-buying-a-book-on-making-friends-in-bollywood%2Farticleshow%2F106870895.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Group%20Offers%20Dharavi%20Residents%20Flats%20With%2017%25%20More%20Space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20Project%20Private%20Limited%20(DRPPL)%2C%20a%20joint%20project%20between%20Adani%20Group%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20today%20announced%20that%20eligible%20residents%20of%20Dharavi%20will%20get%20flats%20with%20a%20minimum%20area%20of%20350%20square%20feet%20with%20independent%20kitchens%20and%20toilets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%2C%20which%20is%20developing%20the%20Dharavi%20slums%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Maharashtra%20Government%2C%20said%20the%20flats%20will%20have%2017%20per%20cent%20more%20space%20and%20extra%20space%20is%20given%20in%20the%20slum%20redevelopment%20projects%20in%20Mumbai.%20In%20such%20places%2C%20the%20maximum%20space%20and%20carpet%20area%20will%20be%20given%20in%20the%20Dharavi%20project%2C%20which%20is%20the%20highest%20compared%20to%20other%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20new%20flats%20will%20be%20dream%20homes%20for%20all%20Dharavi%20residents%20and%20will%20raise%20their%20standard%20of%20living.%20Each%20home%20will%20reflect%20the%20spirit%20of%20Dharaviites%2C%20whose%20aspirations%20will%20always%20be%20the%20same%20as%20ordinary%20Mumbaikars.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20fulfilling%20the%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Dharavi%20by%20keeping%20it%20intact%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20DRPPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanuary%201%2C%202000%2C%20has%20been%20decided%20as%20the%20cut-off%20date%20to%20determine%20eligible%20residents.%20Each%20flat%20will%20have%20a%20separate%20kitchen%20and%20an%20internal%20independent%20toilet%20and%20shall%20be%20safe%20and%20well-ventilated%2C%20DRPPL%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDRPPL%20said%20it%20aims%20to%20transform%20Dharavi%20with%20the%20commercial%20and%20industrial%20complex%20of%20cities%20connected%20to%20the%20world%20while%20keeping%20its%20culture%20of%20awakening%20and%20industrial%20adventure%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20objectives%20of%20the%20redevelopment%20include%3B%20Raising%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20of%20Dharavi%20residents%2C%20opportunities%20in%20the%20economic%20sector%2C%20futuristic%20education%20and%20vocational%20training%2C%20modern%20health%20facilities%20and%20quality%20lifestyle%3A%20all%20these%20will%20be%20available%20in%20Dharavi%20and%20New%20Dharavi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20redeveloped%20project%20will%20also%20have%20a%20community%20hall%2C%20recreational%20area%2C%20public%20garden%2C%20hospital%20and%20day-care%20center%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20ineligible%20residents%20in%20Dharavi%20will%20be%20provided%20housing%20under%20the%20proposed%20affordable%20rental%20housing%20policy%20according%20to%20the%20standards%20prescribed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Maharashtra.%20For%20this%2C%20a%20similar%20development%20plan%20in%20Dharavi%20can%20be%20started%20in%20a%20new%20Dharavi%2C%20DRPPL%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDRPPL%20has%20taken%20up%20the%20challenge%20of%20bringing%20about%20a%20transformation%20in%20Dharavi%20that%20will%20set%20a%20new%20benchmark%20in%20slum%20redevelopment-rehabilitation%20and%20urban%20regeneration%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20All%20these%20will%20be%20benchmarked%20with%20best%20practices%20followed%20for%20similar%20housing%20in%20Singapore%20and%20other%20modern%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705325940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ft0fcijjg_dharavi_625x300_20_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdharavi-residents-to-get-new-flats-with-17-more-space-4868000%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20Project%20Private%20Limited%2C%20a%20joint%20project%20between%20Adani%20Group%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20today%20announced%20that%20eligible%20residents%20of%20Dharavi%20will%20get%20flats%20with%20a%20minimum%20area%20of%20350%20square%20feet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdharavi-residents-to-get-new-flats-with-17-more-space-4868000%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdharavi-residents-to-get-new-flats-with-17-more-space-4868000%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdharavi-residents-to-get-new-flats-with-17-more-space-4868000%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20Things%20the%20BJP%20Wants%20You%20to%20Overlook%20While%20It%20Misdirects%20Focus%20On%20the%20Ram%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11102438%2FScreenshot-2024-01-11-at-10.24.0.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20is%20going%20to%20be%20consecrated%20on%20January%2022%2C%20is%20being%20built%20after%20the%20demolition%20of%20a%20mosque%20at%20the%20same%20place%2C%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20Hindu%20deity%20who%20is%20described%20as%20the%20epitome%20of%20virtues.%20The%20act%20of%20demolition%2C%20described%20by%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20criminal%2C%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20political%20organisations%20who%20believe%20in%20Hindutva.%20The%20land%20was%20given%20to%20them%20by%20the%20same%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20building%20a%20temple.%20Yet%20again%20political%20organisations%20have%20taken%20over%20and%20want%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%20The%20role%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20as%20a%20political%20organisation%20is%20understandable%20but%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20involved%20the%20entire%20government%20paraphernalia%20in%20this%20process.%20The%20money%20being%20spent%20to%20make%20it%20a%20special%20event%20is%20sheer%20madness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20when%20did%20it%20become%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20job%20to%20build%20temples%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20country%20which%20abides%20by%20a%20secular%20constitution%3F%20The%20prime%20minister%20is%20going%20around%20as%20the%20chief%20priest%20of%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20God%20created%20humans.%20But%20consider%20the%20arrogance%20of%20Brahminical%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20probably%20the%20only%20such%20religion%20on%20earth%2C%20which%20believes%20it%20can%20infuse%20life%20into%20a%20God%E2%80%99s%20statue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E1.%20Last%20year%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20lit%2022.23%20lakh%20earthen%20lamps%20in%20Ayodhya%20during%20%E2%80%98Deepotsav%E2%80%99%2C%20something%20started%20by%20him%20after%20he%20assumed%20the%20post.%20He%20even%20bettered%20his%20own%20record%20of%20lighting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-ayodhya-mythical-ram-sita-touch-down-in-helicopter-for-grand-diwali-celebrations%2Fstory-gMzvD3q6GN6U6nDYTV2luK.html%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3E17%20lakh%20lamps%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGuinness%20Book%20of%20World%20Records%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20year%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20colossal%20wastage%20makes%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20whom%20