ampions%20Trophy-winning%20teams%20was%20unhappy%20with%20the%20unruly%20behaviour%20of%20the%20passenger%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vikram%20Reveals%20This%202006%20Film%20Was%20Based%20On%20Triangle%20With%20Sushmita%20And%20His%20Wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFilmmaker%20Vikram%20Bhatt%2C%20best%20known%20for%20his%20thrillers%2C%20often%20made%20headlines%20in%20the%20late%2090s%20and%20early%202000s%20for%20his%20relationships.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40SiddharthKannanOfficial%5C%22%3ESiddharth%20Kannan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Vikram%20Bhatt%20was%20asked%20whether%20his%202006%20film%20%3Cem%3EAnkahee%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20based%20on%20his%20own%20life.%20To%20this%2C%20the%20director%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CQuite%20a%20bit.%20I%20would%20say%20semi-fictionalised.%E2%80%9D%20When%20asked%20if%20the%20film%20was%20based%20on%20his%20relationship%20with%20former%20Miss%20Universe%20and%20Bollywood%20star%20Sushmita%20Sen%2C%20Vikram%20Bhatt%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20%5Bit%20was%20based%5D%20on%20my%20situation%20with%20Sushmita%20and%20my%20wife.%20It%20was%20not%20incident-based.%20Sometimes%20you%20take%20the%20emotion%20and%20fictionalise%20it.%20So%20it%20was%20a%20real%20emotion%20in%20a%20fictionalised%20world.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20his%20ex-wife%20Aditi%20Bhatt%20was%20not%20upset%20with%20their%20lives%20being%20used%20as%20inspiration%20for%20cinema%2C%20Vikram%20Bhatt%20said%20in%20Hindi%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20only%20blamed%20myself%20in%20the%20movie.%20Not%20Sushmita%20or%20my%20ex-wife's%20character.%20So%20why%20be%20upset%3F%20I%20have%20the%20right%20to%20blame%20myself.%E2%80%9D%20About%20Sushmita%20being%20upset%20with%20him%20over%20the%20film%2C%20Vikram%20Bhatt%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don't%20know.%20I%20have%20never%20asked%20her.%20But%20I%20have%20all%20the%20rights%20over%20my%20own%20life%20and%20my%20own%20story%20%E2%80%93%20not%20on%20anyone%20else's%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20his%20tumultuous%20relationships%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20including%20the%20much-publicised%20ones%20with%20Sushmita%20Sen%20and%20Ameesha%20Patel%20%E2%80%93%20had%20left%20him%20exhausted%2C%20Vikram%20Bhatt%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20my%20relationships%20have%20taught%20me%20something.%20The%20pain%20has%20brought%20me%20to%20where%20I%20am%20today.%20My%20spiritual%20journey%20would%20not%20have%20been%20the%20same%20had%20I%20not%20gone%20through%20those%20events.%20I%20believe%20that%20we%20all%20choose%20our%20lessons%20before%20we%20are%20born%20and%20I%20think%20I%20chose%20these.%20And%20I%20say%20it%20with%20honesty%20that%20you%20have%20to%20own%20every%20part%20of%20your%20life.%20Everything%20that%20has%20happened%20is%20my%20decision.%20I%20let%20it%20happen.%20Nothing%20that%20has%20happened%20to%20me%20has%20happened%20without%20my%20permission.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20that%20he%20does%20not%C2%A0regret%C2%A0his%20relationship%20with%20Sushmita%20Sen%2C%20Vikram%20Bhatt%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don't%20regret%20anything%20in%20my%20life.%20Not%20one%20thing.%20Not%20one%20mistake.%20I%20have%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20mistakes%E2%80%A6%20This%20is%20my%20journey.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikram%20Bhatt%20married%20art%20connoisseur%20Shwetambari%20Soni%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705321920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fmntd4umg_alia-_625x300_15_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fvikram-bhatt-opens-up-about-his-situation-with-sushmita-sen-the-inspiration-for-ankahee-4867062%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vikram%20Bhatt%20shared%20that%20his%20film%20Ankahee%2C%20while