ny.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20special%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20recorded%20face-to-face%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Monday%2C%20January%C2%A0%2015%2C%20a%20week%20before%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Jyotish%20Peeth%20explained%20in%20detail%20why%20he%20will%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FqkSAOYTSgYo%3Fsi%3D9bHXUY3iUps6jOHJ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20leave%20you%20to%20get%20the%20details%20from%20the%20interview%2C%20where%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20in%20Hindi%20and%20the%20questions%20are%20a%20mixture%20of%20English%20and%20Hindi.%20However%2C%20let%20me%20in%20broad%20terms%20point%20out%20that%20Swami%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20argument%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20against%20the%20dharma%20shastras%20to%20perform%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20of%20a%20murti%20before%20the%20temple%20is%20complete.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20mahurat%20has%20not%20been%20correctly%20chosen%20revealing%20that%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20Jyotish%20in%20Kashi%20was%20told%20to%20identify%20a%20mahurat%20in%20January%20rather%20than%20the%20most%20appropriate%20mahurat%20for%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20made%20clear%20that%20he%20is%20not%20anti-Modi%20but%20accepted%20that%20the%20building%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20as%20well%20as%20the%20propaganda%20surrounding%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20have%20politicised%20the%20temple.%20He%20said%20he%20completely%20agreed%20with%20comments%20made%20by%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20and%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20January%2014%20where%20the%20Shankaracharya%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CPoliticians%20have%20their%20limits%20and%20they%20have%20responsibility%20under%20the%20Constitution.%20There%20are%20rules%20and%20restrictions%20in%20the%20religious%20and%20spiritual%20domain%20and%20these%20rules%20should%20be%20followed.%20Interfering%20in%20every%20area%20by%20politicians%20is%20insanity%E2%80%A6overstepping%20these%20rules%20for%20propagating%20one%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20an%20act%20of%20rebellion%20against%20God.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20was%20hinting%20at%20Modi%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Jyotish%20Peeth%20said%20nothing%20has%20been%20hidden%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20quite%20clear%20that%20the%20reference%20is%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20was%20asked%20how%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20who%20Hindus%20view%20as%20Maryada%20Purushottam%2C%20would%20view%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20his%20name%20at%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha.%20The%20Swami%20agreed%20that%20he%20is%20worried%20that%20the%20politicization%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20is%20dividing%20India%20rather%20than%20uniting%20India%20and%20also%20creating%20divisions%20among%20its%20Hindu%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati%20was%20asked%20whether%20he%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20temples%20replacing%20existing%20mosques%20in%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20and%20said%20that%20that%20the%20issue%20should%20be%20resolved%20by%20consensus%20with%20wise%20Hindus%20and%20wise%20Muslims%20sitting%20together%20and%20people%20returning%20to%20each%20other%20what%20has%20been%20wrongly%20taken%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20was%20asked%20questions%20about%20himself.%20He%20responded%20to%20claims%20that%20he%20is%20the%20one%20who%20is%20politicizing%20the%20temple%20as%20well%20as%20online%20fake%20claims%20that%20he%20has%20visited%20the%20Ajmer%20Sharif%20Dargah%20to%20spread%20a%20chadhar.%20He%20also%20responded%20to%20the%20accusation%20that%20he%20is%20behaving%20and%20speaking%20like%20a%20Congressman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20being%20very%20careful%20in%20paraphrasing%20the%20broad%20points%20made%20by%20the%20Shankaracharya%20because%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20misinterpret%20him%20or%20convey%20a%20wrong%20impression%20of%20his%20views.%20Inevitably%20that%20will%20mislead%20but%20also%20add%20to%20the%20confusion%20and%20politicisation%20of%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20best%20that%20you%20should%20see%20this%20interview%20for%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20lengthy%2040-minute%20interview%20and%20I%20believe%20the%20first%20by%20any%20of%20the%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20where%20he%20explains%20at%20such%20length%20his%20views%20on%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20the%20politicisation%20that%20is%20happening%20as%20well%20as%20other%20associated%20matters%20such%20as%20whether%20temples%20should%20replace%20mosques%20in%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20and%20how%20he%20responds%20to%20criticism%20of%20himself%2C%20both%20online%20and%20made%20by%20BJP%20supporters%20and%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20what%20I%20will%20do%20is%20to%20give%20you%20the%20list%20of%20questions%20so%20you%20can%20both%20see%20the%20range%20of%20issues%20covered%20and%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20interview%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Why%20have%20you%20refused%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20next%20Monday%2C%20January%2022%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20In%20a%20video%20that%20has%20gone%20viral%20you%20have%20said%20I%20am%20not%20anti-Modi%20but%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20anti-dharma%20shastra%20either.%20Can%20you%20explain%20why%20it%20will%20be%20against%20the%20shastras%20if%20you%20attend%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20The%20temple%20is%20not%20complete%20and%20will%20not%20be%20for%20perhaps%20two%20more%20years.%20Even%20its%20%3Cem%3Eshikar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(spire)%20has%20not%20been%20built.%20Do%20the%20shastras%20permit%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20to%20take%20place%20in%20an%20unfinished%20and%20incomplete%20temple%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20What%20about%20garbhagriha%2Fmahurat%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4)%20What%20about%20the%20other%20three%20Shankaracharyas%20from%20Puri%2C%20Dwarka%20and%20Sringeri%3F%20Will%20they%20be%20attending%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%3F%20Or%20have%20all%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20refused%20the%20invitation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5)%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20central%20person%20at%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20will%20be%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20Speaking%20about%20this%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20has%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9COur%20scriptures%20have%20clearly%20mentioned%20who%20can%20touch%20the%20idol.%20What%20will%20I%20do%20there%20during%20the%20consecration%3F%20Modi%20ji%20will%20inaugurate%20and%20touch%20the%20idol.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20stand%20there%20and%20clap%20to%20applaud%20him.%20I%20know%20the%20dignity%20of%20my%20position.%20This%20isn%E2%80%99t%20ego.%E2%80%9D%20Do%20you%20share%20that%20view%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6)%C2%A0%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20has%20become%20a%20rajnitik%20event%20rather%20than%20a%20dharmik%20event.%20How%20do%20you%20view%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7)%C2%A0%20On%20Saturday%20in%20Bengal%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CPoliticians%20have%20their%20limits%20and%20they%20have%20responsibility%20under%20the%20Constitution.%20There%20are%20rules%20and%20restrictions%20in%20the%20religious%20and%20spiritual%20domain%20and%20these%20rules%20should%20be%20foll