3212236%2Fanganwadi.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnganwadi%20workers%20are%20agitating%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20for%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20be%20addressed%20%E2%80%93%20from%20increase%20of%20wages%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20pension%20to%20other%20retirement%20benefits%20and%20regularisation%20of%20their%20services.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20protests%20are%20also%20stemming%20from%20their%20anger%20towards%20increased%20push%20of%20digitisation%20under%20the%20PM-Poshan%20Abhiyaan%2C%20where%20Anganwadis%E2%80%99%20role%20of%20caregivers%20has%20been%20turned%20into%20that%20of%20data%20collectors.%20The%20honorarium%20paid%20to%20Anganwadi%20workers%20has%20also%20been%20linked%20to%20data%20entry%20into%20various%20apps%20under%20the%20PM-Poshan%20Abhiyaan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20333px)%2085vw%2C%20333px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22333%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3EA%20World%20Bank-assisted%20programme%2C%20PM-Poshan%20Abhiyaan%20aim%20to%20decrease%20stunting%20among%20children%20and%20reduce%20anaemia%20among%20women%20to%20reduce%20low%20birth%20weight.%20Anganwadi%20workers%20play%20an%20important%20role%20to%20provide%20early%20care%20for%20pregnant%20women%2C%20along%20with%20child%20care%2C%20by%20providing%20nutritious%20food%20and%20educating%20children%20in%20pre-schools.%20For%20this%20work%2C%20Anganwadi%20workers%20are%20paid%20a%20honorarium%20of%20around%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month%2C%20while%20Anganwadi%20helpers%20are%20paid%20Rs%207%2C000%20per%20month.%20The%20latter%20are%20considered%20volunteers%20under%20the%20Integrated%20Child%20Development%20Services%20(ICDS)%20Scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20PM-Poshan%20Abhiyaan%20scheme%20introduced%20digitisation%20of%20all%20activities%20of%20Anganwadis%20using%20mobile%20application%20technologies.%20This%20digitisation%20process%20started%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubdocs.worldbank.org%2Fen%2F341341582314668056%2FNote-1-Mobile-Technology-for-Nutrition.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EICDS%20%E2%80%93%20Common%20Application%20Software%20(CAS)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20pushed%20for%20digitisation%20of%20nutrition%20monitoring%20and%20growth%20monitoring%20of%20children%2C%20by%20facilitating%20data%20collection%20for%20decision%20making.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ICDS-CAS%20was%20augmented%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20PM%20Poshan%20Tracker%2C%20which%20brought%20in%20a%20new%20paradigm%20of%20360%C2%B0%20profiling%20of%20Anganwadis%20and%20real-time%20data%20collection.%20The%20idea%20of%20real-time%20data%20collection%20was%20to%20function%20as%20a%20feedback%20mechanism%20to%20help%20improve%20local%20decision%20making.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15123232%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-12.32.26%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15123232%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-12.32.26%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15123232%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-12.32.26%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x214.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15123232%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-12.32.26%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x731.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692987%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22857%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EApplication%20flow%20of%20the%20ICDS-CAS%20mobile%20application.%20Photo%3A%20World%20Bank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20push%20for%20PM%20Poshan%20Tracker%20increased%20data%20collection%20by%20Anganwadis%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poshantracker.in%2Fpdf%2FResources%2FPoshan_Tracker_19_9.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eevery%20update%20of%20the%20application%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20various%20modules%20for%20pregnant%20women%2C%20lactating%20mothers%2C%20children%20of%20different%20age%20groups%20and%20adolescent%20girls%2C%20the%20app%20increased%20the%20burden%20of%20data%20collection%20from%20the%20Anganwadis%20to%20track%20real-time%20daily%20attendance%20and%20monitoring.%20Workers%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20are%20being%20constantly%20pressured%20to%20fill%20the%20application%20every%20day%20to%20show%20%E2%80%9C100%25%20statistics%E2%80%9D%20by%20their%20supervisors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15123436%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-12.34.30%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15123436%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-12.34.30%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15123436%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-12.34.30%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x181.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15123436%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-12.34.30%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x616.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692989%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM-Poshan%20Tracker%20app%20flow.%20Source%3A%20PM%20Poshan%20Tracker%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poshantracker.in%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20PM-Poshan%20Abhiyaan%2C%20Anganwadi%20workers%20were%20provided%20smart%20phones%20under%20the%20ICDS%20budget%20with%20a%20price%20cap%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.nic.in%2Fposhan%2FPoshanTracker%2FClarification_Smartphone_Cost_03-06-2021.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERs%208%2C000%20per%20mobile%20device%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20were%20later%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FLetter-Dated-18-10-2023-Revised-Cost-of-Smartphone.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erevised%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20device%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FLetter%2520dated%252028-03-2023%2520to%2520States_UTs-%2520Specifications%2520of%2520Smart%2520phone_0.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eupdated%20specifications%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20These%20mobile%20devices%20which%20can%20only%20be%20procured%20through%20the%20Government%20e-Marketplace%20(GEM)%20and%20have%20consistently%20failed%20to%20function%20leading%20to%20Anganwadi%20workers%20being%20unable%20to%20enrol%20the%20beneficiaries%20and%20enter%20data%20that%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20collect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20threats%20of%20being%20removed%20from%20work%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20payment%20of%20honorarium%20for%20being%20unable%20to%20upload%20data%20through%20broken%20phones%2C%20the%20Anganwadi%20workers%20in%20Maharashtra%20approached%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20seeking%20relief.%20The%20court%20taking%20the%20issue%20of%20broken%20smartphones%20into%20consideration%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fhc-asks-state-to-give-smartphones-with-poshan-tracker-app-to-anganwadi-workers-8567857%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eordered%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20government%20of%20Maharashtra%20to%20replace%20them%20with%20functional%20ones.%20The%20ICDS%20authorities%20also%20installed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.android.com%2Fintl%2Fen_in%2Fenterprise%2Fmanagement%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emobile-device%20management%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(MDM)%20tracking%20software%20to%20track%20all%20action%20performed%20by%20Anganwadis%20on%20these%20phones%20in%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20litigation%2C%20the%20Anganwadi%20workers%20highlighted%20accessibility%20issues%20of%20the%20mobile%20application%20%E2%80%93%20the%20apps%20are%20only%20available%20in%20English%20and%20not%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fnews-updates%2Fbombay-high-court-anganwadi-centres-food-grains-aadhaar-data-poshan-tracker-application-203188%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Marathi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20ICDS%20Commissioner%20and%20government%20of%20Maharashtra%20even%20opposed%20this%20as%20they%20wanted%20the%20Anganwadi%20workers%20to%20enter%20names%20of%20beneficiaries%20in%20English%20for%20the%20de-duplication%20process%20powered%20by%20Aadhaar.%20This%20strange%20assertion%20in%20courts%20that%20they%20can%20only%20de-duplicate%20beneficiaries%20in%20English%20shows%20how%20the%20state%20itself%20does%20not%20understand%20Aadhaar%20and%20how%20to%20apply%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Anganwadi%20workers%20in%20Maharashtra%20have%20been%20fighting%20against%20ICDS%20software%20applications%20in%20courts%2C%20their%20counterparts%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20have%20been%20similarly%20struggling%20with%20increased%20burden%20of%20these%20new%20applications.%20In%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20beyond%20the%20PM-Poshan%20Tracker%2C%20workers%20are%20required%20to%20use%20an%20array%20of%20other%20mobile%20applications%20to%20create%20indents%20for%20supplies%20like%20eggs%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.emartu.vijaya_app%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emilk%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20other%20food%20supplies%20from%20the%20government%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20as%20part%20of%20their%20real-time%20governance%20strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20been%20constant%20complaints%20from%20workers%20on%20how%20these%20mobile%20applications%20and%20their%20servers%20do%20not%20often%20function.%20The%20Anganwadi%20workers%20are%20being%20asked%20to%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20to%20upload%20data%20on%20apps%2C%20as%20the%20servers%20are%20not%20busy%20during%20the%20night.%20For%20the%20Child%20Development%20Project%20Officers%20and%20supervisors%2C%20unless%20the%20data%20on%20daily%20attendance%20and%20work%20has%20been%20collected%2C%20the%20Anganwadi%20workers%20have%20not%20completed%20their%20work%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20distribution%20of%20mobile%20phones%20to%20Anganwadi%20workers%20means%20that%20they%20have%20to%20be%20constantly%20available%20over%20phone%20to%20respond%20in%20real-time%20to%20the%20supervisors.%20These%20supervisors%20who%20look%20at%20their%20dashboards%20everyday%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20want%20to%20ensure%20the%20pre-schools%20open%20on%20time%2C%20attendance%20of%20kids%20is%20recorded%20on%20time%20and%20every%20other%20activity%20happens%20on%20time%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20core%20aspect%20of%20real-time%20governance%20being%20employed%20by%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20government%20of%20India.%20For%20real-time%20governance%20to%20occur%2C%20workers%20have%20to%20be%20available%20to%20work%20real-time.%20But%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20focus%20on%20work%20with%20broken%20apps%20and%20pressure%20from%20supervisors%20to%20constantly%20log%20work.%20Real-time%20governance%20demands%20workers%20act%20as%20robots%20who%20are%20constantly%20doing%20their%20task%20while%20responding%20to%20instructions%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20constant%20push%20for%20the%20Anganwadi%20workers%20to%20collect%20new%20forms%20of%20data%2C%20the%20PM-Poshan%20Tracker%20has%20new%20modules%20to%20create%20health%20IDs%20of%20every%20beneficiary%20under%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Digital%20Mission.%20All%20the%20data%20collected%20about%20children%20and%20pregnant%20women%20is%20now%20being%20stored%20using%20electronic%20health%20records.%20The%20creation%20of%20beneficiary%20profiles%20is%20the%20core%20aspect%20of%20360%C2%B0%20profiling%20being%20imposed%20by%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15144641%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-2.46.36%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15144641%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-2.46.36%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201198w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15144641%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-2.46.36%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x174.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15144641%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-2.46.36%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x593.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693011%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22694%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM-Poshan%20Tracker%20app%20flow.%20Source%3A%20PM%20Poshan%20Tracker%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poshantracker.in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Anganwadi%20workers%20have%20been%20given%20a%20new%20task%20of%20collecting%20facial%20biometrics%20of%20every%20beneficiary%20and%20to%20use%20them%20for%20authentication%20using%20facial%20recognition.%20The%20push%20away%20from%20Aadhaar%20to%20facial%20recognition%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20have%20been%20primarily%20because%20of%20the%20failures%20and%20fraud%20emerging%20from%20fingerprint%20recognition%20with%20Aadhaar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnganwadi%20workers%20have%20been%20facing%20a%20hard%20time%20in%20collecting%20and%20authenticating%20using%20AP%E2%80%99s%20facial%20recognition%20system%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapfrs.ap.gov.in%2Ffrs-help-videos%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAP-FRS%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20One%20of%20their%20demands%2C%20part%20of%20the%20protests%2C%20is%20to%20stop%20imposing%20the%20facial%20recognition%20system%20for%20beneficiary%20identification.%20A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fanganwadi-workers-in-andhra-pradesh-threaten-to-boycott-face-recognition-system%2Farticle67372378.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%20from%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ehighlights%20how%20this%20system%20has%20been%20failing%2C%20leading%20to%20pregnant%20women%20being%20forced%20to%20walk%20to%20the%20Anganwadi%20centre%2C%20for%20authentication%2C%20if%20the%20FRS%20is%20unable%20to%20authenticate%20them%20on%20the%20field.%20The%20constant%20failures%20in%20authenticating%20beneficiaries%20means%20Anganwadi%20workers%20need%20to%20work%20longer.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWorkers%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20upload%20data%20into%20multiple%20apps%20by%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments.%20This%20has%20increased%20their%20work%20further%20with%20no%20data%20sharing%20agreements%20between%20the%20Union%20and%20states.%20The%20Anganwadi%20workers%20also%20maintain%20a%20physical%20ledger%20as%20these%20apps%20do%20not%20function%20all%20the%20time.%20This%20breeds%20a%20complex%20web%20of%20multiple%20records.%20One%20of%20the%20demands%20from%20Anganwadi%20workers%20is%20to%20create%20a%20single%20app%20instead%20of%20demands%20of%20multiple%20entries%20into%20different%20apps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20the%20data%20collection%20the%20workers%20are%20being%20additionally%20forced%20to%20conduct%20promotional%20activities%20by%20the%20government%20like%20Yoga%20Day.%20These%20new%20events%20and%20activities%20are%20added%20as%20new%20modules%20in%20the%20apps.%20The%20state%20continues%20to%20track%20whether%20these%20activities%20have%20been%20conducted%20or%20not%20through%20various%20apps%2C%20demanding%20digital%20evidence%20of%20participation%20of%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15154556%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-3.45.28%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15154556%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-3.45.28%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15154556%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-3.45.28%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x175.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15154556%2FScreenshot-2024-01-15-at-3.45.28%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x596.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693027%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22699%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM-Poshan%20Tracker%20app%20flow.%20Source%3A%20PM-Poshan%20Tracker%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poshantracker.in%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContrary%20to%20popular%20beliefs%20of%20technology%20improving%20and%20easing%20the%20work%20for%20Anganwadi%20workers%2C%20these%20apps%20have%20had%20the%20opposite%20effect.%20The%20applications%20and%20various%20modules%20of%20the%20application%20constantly%20demand%20new%20forms%20of%20work%20from%20workers%20who%20are%20not%20trained%20under%20these%20tasks.%20These%20issues%20are%20universal%20for%20Anganwadi%20workers%20across%20India%2C%20who%20have%20been%20protesting%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20amount%20of%20work%20is%20being%20increased%20with%20every%20new%20module%20added%20into%20apps%2C%20the%20workers%E2%80%99%20wages%20have%20stagnated.%20Anganwadi%20workers%20are%20treated%20as%20volunteers%20who%20are%20signing%20for%20a%20voluntary%20activity%2C%20but%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20work%20like%20a%20full-time%20worker.%20They%20are%20not%20being%20provided%20any%20health%2C%20insurance%20or%20retirement%20benefits%20for%20this%20work%20either.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20demands%20of%20Anganwadi%20workers%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20is%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20receive%20government%20schemes%20that%20are%20being%20provided%20to%20the%20general%20population.%20With%20360%C2%B0%20profiling%20of%20households%2C%20any%20government%20employee%20household%20is%20automatically%20rejected%20for%20any%20state%20welfare%20schemes.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Anganwadi%20workers%2C%20they%20are%20treated%20as%20government%20employees%20and%20cannot%20get%20state%20welfare.%20At%20the%20same%20time%20they%20are%20treated%20as%20volunteers%20and%20do%20not%20get%20employee%20benefits.%20This%20is%20what%20the%20workers%20are%20fighting%20for%2C%20to%20not%20be%20excluded%20by%20the%20state%20in%20every%20aspect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705311426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F03212236%2Fanganwadi.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fanganwadi-worker-protest-maharashtra-poshan-tracker%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20amount%20of%20work%20for%20them%20is%20being%20increased%20with%20every%20new%20module%20added%20into%20unwieldy%20apps%2C%20the%20workers'%20wages%20have%20stagnated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fanganwadi-worker-protest-maharashtra-poshan-tracker%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22February%208%20polls%20can't%20be%20postponed%3A%20Pakistan%20election%20commission%20tells%20Senate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705310683000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106862099%2Cimgsize-501009.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fresolution-to-delay-february-8-polls-in-pakistan-senate-islamabad-news%2Farticleshow%2F106861970.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3