3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHerald%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20among%20other%20outlets%20to%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Khestra%20Trust%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20follow%20the%20500%20year%20old%20traditions%20in%20worshipping%20and%20observing%20the%20rituals%20in%20the%20proposed%20consecration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98The%20puja%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lala%20is%20done%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Ramanandi%20tradition%20but%20the%20Trust%20is%20following%20a%20mixed%20tradition%2C%20which%20is%20not%20proper%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Mahant%20said.%20%E2%80%9DWe%20want%20the%20rituals%20and%20worship%20of%20Ram%20Lala%20to%20continue%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Ramanandi%20traditions%20but%20the%20Trust%20has%20ignored%20our%20plea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20emphasised%20that%20the%20%E2%80%99tilak%E2%80%99%20and%20other%20symbols%20in%20the%20Ramanandi%20traditions%20were%20different%20from%20other%20sects.%20This%20sect%20has%20been%20responsible%20for%20conducting%20the%20prayers%20in%20the%20make-shift%20temple%20that%20has%20existed%20in%20Ayodhya%20since%20December%201992%20and%20before%20that%2C%20on%20the%20Ram%20chabutra%2C%20the%20outer%20courtyard%20of%20the%20Babri%20masjid%2C%20when%20the%20mosque%20still%20stood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20also%20reports%20that%20the%20Nirmohi%20Akhara%20had%20pleaded%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20it%20should%20also%20be%20given%20the%20right%20to%20hold%20puja%20and%20other%20rituals%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%20The%20court%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Trust%2C%20which%20would%20look%20after%20the%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20might%2C%20if%20it%20wanted%2C%20give%20it%20the%20right.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amarujala.com%2Fram-mandir%2Fayodhya-ram-mandir-champat-rai-said-that-temple-belongs-to-ramanand-sect-not-to-shaiva-shakta-and-sannyasis-2024-01-08%3FpageId%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EAmar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EUjala%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Temple%20Trust%2C%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20method%20of%20worship%20in%20the%20new%20temple%20had%20said%20that%20since%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20Ram%20temple%2C%20Ramanand%20tradition%20will%20be%20followed.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20temple%20belongs%20to%20the%20Ramanand%20sect%2C%20and%20not%20to%20the%20Sanyasis%2C%20not%20to%20Shaiva%20or%20Shakta%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%20This%20had%20created%20considerable%20distruct%20with%20Shankatracharyas%20openly%20asking%20why%20it%20was%20not%20being%20%E2%80%9Chanded%20over%20to%20the%20Ramanandi%20sect%20then%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShankaracharya%20Nishchalananda%20Saraswati%2C%20who%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2Fjan%2F05%2Fpuri-seer-says-wont-visit-ayodhya-says-rituals-must-conform-to-shastras-2648076.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20confirmed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20going%20to%20Ayodhya%20for%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpm-modi-to-unveil-ayodhya-ram-temple-on-jan-22-2024-temple-trusts-appeal-sparks-speculation%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJanuary%2022%20event%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20criticised%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20advising%20him%20not%20to%20diminish%20his%20stature%20while%20holding%20a%20position%20of%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENo%20date%20for%20complete%20construction%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERai%20had%20also%20said%20candidly%20that%20there%20was%20no%20end-date%20to%20when%20the%20temple%20construction%20would%20be%20completed%2C%20and%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20hurry%20to%20complete%20the%20construction%20work%2C%20as%20it%20took%2018%20months%20to%20build%20only%20the%20foundation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20the%20idea%20was%20that%20it%20would%20be%20built%20in%2018%20months%E2%80%A6%20so%2C%20the%20foundation%20could%20be%20built%20in%2018%20months.%20The%20idea%20was%20that%20it%20would%20be%20built%20in%20three%20years.%20If%20we%20start%20from%20July%202020%2C%20then%20with%202023%2C%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years%20have%20passed.%20Now%2C%20if%20someone%20decides%20that%20it%20will%20be%20completed%20within%20a%20year%2C%20then%20after%20a%20year%2C%20he%20will%20have%20to%20tell%20that%20so%20much%20is%20still%20incomplete%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAmar%20Ujala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can%20read%20more%20about%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fits-a-ram-mandir-ramanand-tradition-to-be-followed-temple-trusts-secy-remarks-draw-criticism%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705302056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11102438%2FScreenshot-2024-01-11-at-10.24.0.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fram-lala-ramanandi-nirmohi-akhali-temple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reports%20say%20the%20Nirmohi%20Akhada%2C%20a%20key%20player%20in%20this%20context%20and%20an%20original%20litigant%20in%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi-Babri%20Masjid%20title%20dispute%20is%20feeling%20sidelined%20and%20saying%20the%20'tilak'%20and%20other%20symbols%20in%20the%20Ramanandi%20traditions%20were%20different%20from%20other%20sects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fram-lala-ramanandi-nirmohi-akhali-temple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yemen%3A%20US%20shoots%20down%20m