ed%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20entrusted%20with%20the%20duties%20of%20taking%20care%20of%20my%20siblings%20%E2%80%94%20from%20waking%20them%20up%2C%20taking%20them%20to%20school%2C%20and%20helping%20them%20finish%20their%20homework%20to%20feeding%20them%20and%20putting%20them%20to%20sleep%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirija%20never%20entered%20the%20kitchen%20until%201968%2C%20which%20is%20when%20she%20got%20married.%20Her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20family%20comprised%20100%20members%2C%20and%20the%2018-year-old%20bride%20was%20asked%20to%20fry%20%3Cem%3Epapadum%3C%2Fem%3Es%20for%20them.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20never%20cooked%20before.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20I%20had%20stepped%20inside%20the%20kitchen.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do%20but%20I%20was%20scared%20to%20tell%20it%20to%20my%20mother-in-law%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FGirija-Paati-1-1704977358.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girija%20says%20she%20prepares%20all%20food%20items%20just%20the%20way%20she%20cooks%20for%20her%20grandchildren.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FGirija-Paati-1-1704977358.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FGirija-Paati-1-1704977358-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FGirija-Paati-1-1704977358-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FGirija-Paati-1-1704977358-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FGirija-Paati-1-1704977358-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338037%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C